<section id="section-location" class="py-16 md:py-24 px-5 md:px-10 bg-white">
  <div class="text-center mb-12 fade-up">
    <div class="font-en text-sm text-primary tracking-[3px] uppercase mb-2.5">Location</div>
    <h3 class="font-en text-[28px] md:text-[38px] font-bold text-dark leading-snug">Luminus <em class="text-primary italic">LOCATION</em></h3>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 md:gap-16 max-w-[1200px] mx-auto items-start fade-up">
    <div class="w-full aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-200 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-muted text-[15px] overflow-hidden">
      <div class="text-center">
        <i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt text-5xl text-primary mb-4 block"></i>
        지도가 표시됩니다
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-1.5">오시는 길</h4>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-dark font-medium mb-7 leading-relaxed">인천 연수구 해돋이로 160-15, 206-211호<br>(송도동, 더퍼스트시티)</p>

      <dl class="mb-8">
        <dt class="text-sm font-bold text-primary-dark mb-1.5 flex items-center gap-1.5"><i class="fas fa-bus text-primary"></i> 대중교통 이용 시</dt>
        <dd class="text-[13px] text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-3.5 pl-1">· 더샵 하버뷰 14단지 (98, 순환41)<br>· 송도 힐스테이트 5단지 (16, 지선 525)</dd>
        <dt class="text-sm font-bold text-primary-dark mb-1.5 flex items-center gap-1.5"><i class="fas fa-subway text-primary"></i> 지하철 이용 시</dt>
        <dd class="text-[13px] text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-3.5 pl-1">· 인천 1호선 인천대입구역 하차 4번 출구, 도보 15분</dd>
        <dt class="text-sm font-bold text-primary-dark mb-1.5 flex items-center gap-1.5"><i class="fas fa-car text-primary"></i> 자가용 이용 시</dt>
        <dd class="text-[13px] text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-3.5 pl-1">· 건물 뒷편 주차장 출입구 통해 주차</dd>
      </dl>

      <table class="w-full border-collapse mb-8">
        <tr><th class="text-left py-2.5 px-3.5 text-sm font-medium text-dark w-[40%] border-b border-gray-100">월요일 - 금요일</th><td class="text-left py-2.5 px-3.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground border-b border-gray-100">09:30 - 20:00</td></tr>
        <tr><th class="text-left py-2.5 px-3.5 text-sm font-medium text-dark w-[40%] border-b border-gray-100">토요일</th><td class="text-left py-2.5 px-3.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground border-b border-gray-100">09:30 - 15:30</td></tr>
        <tr><th class="text-left py-2.5 px-3.5 text-sm font-medium text-dark w-[40%] border-b border-gray-100">점심시간</th><td class="text-left py-2.5 px-3.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground border-b border-gray-100">점심시간 없음</td></tr>
        <tr><th class="text-left py-2.5 px-3.5 text-sm font-medium text-dark w-[40%] border-b border-gray-100">일요일</th><td class="text-left py-2.5 px-3.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground border-b border-gray-100">휴진</td></tr>
      </table>

      <div class="bg-surface p-6 rounded-lg">
        <div class="text-xs text-muted tracking-wide uppercase mb-2">상담 &amp; 문의</div>
        <div class="font-en text-[28px] font-bold text-primary-dark tracking-wide">032.833.9909</div>
        <div class="text-[13px] text-muted mt-1">FAX 032.833.9908</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
